            <item>
                <title>Get the file extension in PHP</title>
                <link>https://www.saikiransripada.com/get-the-file-extension-in-php/</link>
                <content:encoded>
                    <![CDATA[
                    <p>A simple function to get the extension of a file. Meet <a href="https://php.net/pathinfo" target="_blank">pathinfo()</a>.</p>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-php" data-lang="php"><span class="cp">&lt;?php</span> <span class="nv">$extension</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nb">pathinfo</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nv">$filename</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="nx">PATHINFO_EXTENSION</span><span class="p">);</span> <span class="cp">?&gt;</span></code></pre></figure>


